      • distinctByKey

        static <T> Predicate<T> distinctByKey(Function<? super T,Object> keyExtractor)
        Create a "distinct by property" predicate for filtering. Usage: Stream distinct Person objects by name: persons.stream().filter(distinctByKey(p -> p.getName());
        Returns:
        predicate (thread-safe)
